{"tid":401102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十間大學校長發聲明譴責濫用言論自由　不支持港獨","createTime":"2017-09-15T10:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T07:20:22.000Z","uid":41404,"like":8,"dislike":199,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88f407f54bbf80786caae13a33dff9e37ce411df","tid":401102,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:54:52.000Z","msg":"十間大學校長發聲明：譴責濫用言論自由　不支持港獨<br />\n<br />\n十間大學的校長發表聯合聲明指，珍惜言論自由，但譴責最近濫用言論自由的行為，強調言論自由並非絕對，有自由就有責任，並特此聲明不支持「港獨」，認為這是違反基本法。<br />\n<br />\n參與聯署的大學包括城大、浸大、樹仁大學、嶺大、中大、教大、理大、科大、公開大學和港大。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354267-20170915.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354267-20170915.htm&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=6907e2e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354267-20170915.htm&h=62c9f160\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354267-20170915.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f3bfe6dbfc70dfe605ee43314b8e91cdbcf258ff","tid":401102,"uid":44646,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十間大學校長發聲明：譴責濫用言論自由　不支持港獨<br />\n<br />\n十間大學的校長發表聯合聲明指，珍惜言論自由，但譴責最近濫用言論自由的行為，強調言論自由並非絕對，有自由就有責任，並特此聲明不支持「港獨」，認為這是違反基本法。<br />\n<br />\n參與聯署的大學包括城大、浸大、樹仁大學、嶺大、中大、教大、理大、科大、公開大學和港大。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354267-20170915.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354267-20170915.htm&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=6907e2e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354267-20170915.htm&h=62c9f160\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354267-20170915.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n認真，快D貼「一國一制」，一定違反基本法，睇下校長有咩反應"},{"pid":"5d322e59df69ee6aa3754225e859495cd18be49e","tid":401102,"uid":26451,"